&lt;p>Armin Lederer, Lei Zheng, Zhihua Wu, and Tharusha Fonseka look forward to meeting with Prof. Liu to discuss learning-based control, robotics, and safe autonomy.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Learn more about Prof. Liu at &lt;a href="https://homepage.hit.edu.cn/liuyuhan?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://homepage.hit.edu.cn/liuyuhan?lang=en&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Three papers accepted at ICML 2026</title><link>https://scale-nus.github.io/post/20260501-three-papers-accepted-at-icml-2026/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://scale-nus.github.io/post/20260501-three-papers-accepted-at-icml-2026/</guid><description>&lt;p>We got three papers accepted at the International Conference on Machine Learning. You can already check out the preprints &lt;a href="https://openreview.net/pdf?id=9iAfjtz7lE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&lt;/a>, &lt;a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2605.09757" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&lt;/a> and &lt;a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.05355" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&lt;/a>. Looking forward to discussing the papers with you in Seoul!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Two papers accepted at IEEE TAC</title><link>https://scale-nus.github.io/post/20260401-two-papers-accepted-at-ieee-tac/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://scale-nus.github.io/post/20260401-two-papers-accepted-at-ieee-tac/</guid><description>&lt;p>Two papers recently got accepted at the IEEE Transactions on Automatic Control. Check out the papers &lt;a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/11471064" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&lt;/a> and &lt;a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/11141748" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Papers accepted at ECC and ACC 2026</title><link>https://scale-nus.github.io/post/20260301-papers-accepted-at-ecc-and-acc-2026/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://scale-nus.github.io/post/20260301-papers-accepted-at-ecc-and-acc-2026/</guid><description>&lt;p>We got papers accepted at the European Control Conference and 